<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٢٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَجْرَهُ فِي الدُّنْيَا}</span> ... باِلذِّكْرِ الحَسَنِ، وَالوَلَدِ الصَّالِحِ وَالنُّبُوَّةِ فيِ ذُرِّيَّتِه.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٢٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَتَقْطَعُونَ السَّبِيلَ}</span> ... تَقْطَعُونَ طُرُقَ المُسَافِرِينَ بِفِعْلِكُمُ الفَاحِشَةَ بِهِمْ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٢٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نَادِيكُمُ}</span> ... مَجْلِسِكُمُ الَّذِي تَجْتَمِعُونَ فِيهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمُنكَرَ}</span> ... الأَعْمَالَ المُنْكَرَةَ؛ كَالسُّخْرِيَةِ مِنَ النَّاسِ، وَقَذْفِ المَارَّةِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِالْبُشْرَى}</span> ... بِالخَبَرِ السَّارِّ،<span class="c5"> وَهُوَ:</span> البِشَارَةُ بِإِسْحَاقَ - عليه السلام -.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٣٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْغَابِرِينَ}</span> ... البَاقِينَ فيِ العَذَابِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٣٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سِيءَ بِهِمْ}</span> ... سَاءَهُ مَجِيئُهُمْ خَوْفًا عَلَيْهِمْ مِنْ قَوْمِهِ أَنْ يَفْعَلُوا بِهِمُ الفَاحِشَةَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٣٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَضَاقَ بِهِمْ ذَرْعًا}</span> ... ضَاقَ صَدْرُهُ، وَحَزِنَ خَوْفًا عَلَيْهِمْ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٣٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رِجْزًا}</span> ... عَذَابًا شَدِيدًا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٣٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَّرَكْنَا مِنْهَا}</span> ... أَبْقَيْنَا مِنْ دِيَارِهِمُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٣٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{آيَةً بَيِّنَةً}</span> ... آثَارًا وَاضِحَةً.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٣٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَارْجُوا الْيَوْمَ الْآخِرَ}</span> ... اطْلُبُوا بِعِبَادَتِكُمْ جَزَاءَ الآخِرَةِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٣٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَلَا تَعْثَوْا}</span> ... لَا تُكْثِرُوا الفَسَادَ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٣٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الرَّجْفَةُ}</span> ... الزَّلْزَلَةُ الشَّدِيدَةُ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>